---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../../site";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Transfer | We Scale Startups"
  description="Transfer the growth system to the founder, team, agencies, and future hires so the company keeps improving."
  path="/transfer"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Transfer</p>
      <h1>Leave the team with a system they can keep running.</h1>
      <p>We document decisions, workflows, reporting, meeting cadence, and handoff rules so the growth function gets stronger after the engagement ends.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a
          class="button button-dark button-with-subcopy"
          href={siteConfig.bookingUrl}
          data-cta="transfer-book"
          title={siteConfig.bookingCallReassurance}
        >
          <span class="button-label">{siteConfig.bookingLabel}</span>
          <span class="button-subcopy">{siteConfig.bookingSubcopy}</span>
        </a>
        <a class="button button-light" href={siteConfig.scorecardUrl} data-cta="transfer-scorecard">
          Or, {siteConfig.scorecardLabel} →
        </a>
        <a class="button button-light" href="/services/fractional-cmo" data-cta="transfer-fcmo">Fractional CMO support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell grid-3">
      <article class="feature-card"><h3>Document</h3><p>Capture the ICP, strategy, assets, reporting, experiments, and decision rules.</p></article>
      <article class="feature-card"><h3>Handoff</h3><p>Give founders, marketers, sales teams, agencies, and future hires a shared operating view.</p></article>
      <article class="feature-card"><h3>Reduce Dependency</h3><p>Make the team less dependent on founder instinct and external operators over time.</p></article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="shell cta-inner">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Plan the handoff</p>
        <h2>Make sure the system survives after the engagement.</h2>
        <p>
          In {siteConfig.bookingCallDurationPhrase}, we can map what needs documenting, who owns the rhythm, and whether fractional support or a sprint is the right next shape of help.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a
          class="button button-brand button-with-subcopy"
          href={siteConfig.bookingUrl}
          data-cta="transfer-final-book"
          title={siteConfig.bookingCallReassurance}
        >
          <span class="button-label">{siteConfig.bookingLabel}</span>
          <span class="button-subcopy">{siteConfig.bookingSubcopy}</span>
        </a>
        <a class="button button-light" href={siteConfig.scorecardUrl} data-cta="transfer-final-scorecard">
          Or, {siteConfig.scorecardLabel} →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
